{"id":17929,"date":"2024-02-24T20:48:09","date_gmt":"2020-12-24T15:18:09","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=17929"},"modified":"2023-05-23T09:14:54","modified_gmt":"2023-05-23T03:44:54","slug":"balcony-safety-grill-designs","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/balcony-safety-grill-designs\/","title":{"rendered":"Eight Balcony Safety Grill Designs For Apartments For A Secure Outdoor Space"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>Safety first: Take your pick from our list of balcony safety grill designs<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>What makes the balcony an invaluable asset to a house, and why do we tend to look more into the design, comfort level and safety of this particular area of our homes? That would be because it is cherished by everyone in the family, no matter which age group. Balconies connect us to the outdoors, which is a vital human need for those living in apartments. These spaces are for you to relax, or for practising early morning meditation and yoga; to unwind with some tea or coffee while reading; or for catching up with your daily dose of social media.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Balconies can indeed be multipurpose. As a part of the house that is accessed by people of all age groups, it is crucial that the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/balcony-grill-designs\/\">balcony grill<\/a> is given due attention during the process of designing. No matter the purpose and the user of your balcony, it needs a well-built and safe grill design. Check out these cool balcony safety grill designs for apartments. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Enclosed Balconies And Big Spaces<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>In such large balconies, you can use the grill design to give the look of an extended room. A fully enclosed space and solid filled grill panels ensure excellent safety. This is one of the most helpful and safe designs if you have children in your house &#8212; you will have one less thing to worry about! An additional benefit of such a safety grill design is the reduction in outside noise and disturbance.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/24204047\/enclosed-balcony-safety-grill-design-photo.jpg\" alt=\"Modern balcony safety grill designed with fully enclosed space and solid filled grill panels ensure excellent safety.\" class=\"wp-image-17935\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/24204047\/enclosed-balcony-safety-grill-design-photo.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/24204047\/enclosed-balcony-safety-grill-design-photo-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/24204047\/enclosed-balcony-safety-grill-design-photo-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/24204047\/enclosed-balcony-safety-grill-design-photo-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Safety grills like these create an additional room on the balcony<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Classic Two-Feet Wall With A Single Safety Bar<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Stunning balcony safety grill design photos look classic and the design ensures maximum safety. The simple, no-frills grill design helps in making the balcony appear like a seamless extension of the attached living room. The design appears very minimalistic, a quality that goes with every kind of home and person. It gives a frame-like outside view, and allows for sufficient ventilation.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/24204034\/balcony-safety-grill-design-with-single-bar.jpg\" alt=\"Beautiful house balcony safety grill designed with two feet wall with a single bar looks minimal but maximum safe.\" class=\"wp-image-17933\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/24204034\/balcony-safety-grill-design-with-single-bar.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/24204034\/balcony-safety-grill-design-with-single-bar-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/24204034\/balcony-safety-grill-design-with-single-bar-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/24204034\/balcony-safety-grill-design-with-single-bar-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Classic safety bars are always a good idea<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"How much does an interior designer cost in india?\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/16115932\/interior-designer-cost-in-india.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Traditional Royal Pillars As Part of Balcony Safety Grill Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This variety of balcony safety grill design never fails to charm. It does not look like a partition, but mere protective fencing. Additionally, you can just rest your foot casually in between the pillars when you are catching a break &#8212; something we all do subconsciously! The design will work especially if you live in suburban areas or homes with large balconies. You don\u2019t have to go with a stereotypical design&nbsp; &#8212; you can always explore more pillar design options!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/24204111\/traditional-house-balcony-safety-grill-design.jpg\" alt=\"Safety balcony grill designed with traditional pillar protection looks charming.\" class=\"wp-image-17939\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/24204111\/traditional-house-balcony-safety-grill-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/24204111\/traditional-house-balcony-safety-grill-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/24204111\/traditional-house-balcony-safety-grill-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/24204111\/traditional-house-balcony-safety-grill-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Traditional pillar protection looks extremely appealing in large balconies<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Wooden And Artsy<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>For medium-size spaces and terrace-like exclusive types of the balcony, a design like this seems apt. You can have a dedicated lobby, and then a beautiful space of your own. As always, wood and plants go great together! The heightened grill\/panel ensures privacy. The modern balcony safety grill design is optimised to provide you with some much required alone time with family.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/24204105\/modern-balcony-safety-grill-design-with-wooden.jpg\" alt=\"Apartment balcony safety grill designed with high wooden is excellent for ensuring privacy and safety.\" class=\"wp-image-17938\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/24204105\/modern-balcony-safety-grill-design-with-wooden.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/24204105\/modern-balcony-safety-grill-design-with-wooden-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/24204105\/modern-balcony-safety-grill-design-with-wooden-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/24204105\/modern-balcony-safety-grill-design-with-wooden-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>High wooden safety grills are great for ensuring privacy<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Not-So-Messy Mesh<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Mesh grills are useful in many ways &#8212; they provide safety and security, and the mesh works great for hanging <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/balcony-decoration-ideas\/\">decor on the balcony<\/a>. The design, though applicable to any room, would be more suited for a bedroom balcony if you plan on the exact same swinging chair and colourful plants theme. Another alternative is to have a regular metal safety grill for your balcony and attach a mesh or a net separately for an additional layer of security.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/24204021\/apartment-balcony-safety-grill-design-with-mesh.jpg\" alt=\"Small balcony with mesh grills provides safety and security is the balcony safety grill designs for apartment.\" class=\"wp-image-17931\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/24204021\/apartment-balcony-safety-grill-design-with-mesh.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/24204021\/apartment-balcony-safety-grill-design-with-mesh-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/24204021\/apartment-balcony-safety-grill-design-with-mesh-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/24204021\/apartment-balcony-safety-grill-design-with-mesh-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Mesh grills are great for balconies with houses that have children and pets<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Petite Spaces And Metal Safety Grills<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>With just enough space for a chair and a small coffee table, you don\u2019t want to feel any more trapped. For such spaces, a balcony safety grill design that is perfect is the usual and highly apt metal grill with horizontal bars across. You can also add a glass panel to the metal grill &#8212; it not only gives an additional layer of security but also helps in making a petite <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/balcony-design\/\">home balcony<\/a> look spacious.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/24204059\/modern-balcony-safety-grill-design.jpg\" alt=\"Small modern balcony safety grill designed in metal with horizontal bars across making a petite balcony look spacious.\" class=\"wp-image-17937\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/24204059\/modern-balcony-safety-grill-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/24204059\/modern-balcony-safety-grill-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/24204059\/modern-balcony-safety-grill-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/24204059\/modern-balcony-safety-grill-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Metal safety grills come in various cool designs<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">The Classic Metal Grill<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Similar to the previous metal safety grill, this design is useful for small spaces and homeowners who wish to maximise such spaces. The metallic grill enhances those otherwise plain walls. This design leaves space for a lot of experimentation: you could use various types of bars for grills, or hang some plants or lanterns on it &#8212; or keep it simple to enjoy an unobstructed view!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/24204040\/classic-metal-balcony-safety-grill-design-for-apartment-.jpg\" alt=\"Small balcony safety grill designed in classic metal enhances the look of space and safety.\" class=\"wp-image-17934\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/24204040\/classic-metal-balcony-safety-grill-design-for-apartment-.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/24204040\/classic-metal-balcony-safety-grill-design-for-apartment--300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/24204040\/classic-metal-balcony-safety-grill-design-for-apartment--768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/24204040\/classic-metal-balcony-safety-grill-design-for-apartment--150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Classic metal grills are among the most preferred modern balcony safety grill design options<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a free design consultation from design cafe\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/27144955\/get-free-design-consultation.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Exquisite Balcony Safety Grill Design With Intricate Detailing<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Patterns on safety grills never fail to impress! The beautiful patterns even create beautiful shadows on the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/balcony-flooring-ideas\/\">floor of the balcony<\/a>. The elegant design of the safety grill makes the balcony look modern and sophisticated, and opens up various possibilities for designing the rest of the space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/24204053\/intricate-detailing-house-balcony-safety-grill-design.jpg\" alt=\"Minimalistic modern balcony safety grill designed in a pattern looks stylish and sophisticated.\" class=\"wp-image-17936\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/24204053\/intricate-detailing-house-balcony-safety-grill-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/24204053\/intricate-detailing-house-balcony-safety-grill-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/24204053\/intricate-detailing-house-balcony-safety-grill-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/24204053\/intricate-detailing-house-balcony-safety-grill-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Safety grills that make pretty-looking balconies<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You can always experiment with balcony safety grill designs, but don\u2019t forget to primarily focus on the safety aspect of the grills!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you enjoyed reading about balcony safety grill designs, also have a look at <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/balcony-wall-design-ideas\/\">balcony wall design ideas<\/a>.<\/p>\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Looking For Functional Interior Designs?<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with smart solutions<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-c